Package: tidyeof
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Empirical Orthogonal Functions and Spatial Downscaling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nicolas", "Gauthier",
    email = "nicolas.gauthier@ufl.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2225-5827"))
Description: An R package for conducting empirical orthogonal function (EOF)
    analysis in the tidyverse framework. Functions to isolate modes of
    variability from spatiotemporal data, run various diagnostics, and use
    these patterns for spatial downscaling via canonical correlation analysis.
